Motormaster left the room with Megatron. He wasnt needed, and had important
buisness to attend to. He arrived where Beastbox, Speedbreaker, and Drag
Strip were. "Speedbreaker, Drag Strip, go find your Stunticon comerades,
and tell them to come back to base now" Motormaster stated, with a low
voice to engrave how serious he was. "Finally" Exclaimed Speedbreaker, who
transformed right there and then. He then drove towards the elevator.
